snippet.title: Cave Digger 2 - Official Mixed Reality Expansion Update Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Cave Digger 2 is an exploration looter shooter developed by VRKiwi. Players will soon be able to access the Mixed Reality Expansion update for the game bringing the ability to mine and collect resources straight from the player's environment with mixed reality. The Mixed Reality Expansion update for Cave Digger 2 launches on June 27 for Meta Quest 3.
